  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc8 : \u0ba4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc6\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1 599 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bcd 123 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9f\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bc0\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Kandakkadu Rehabilitation Center Unrest: 599 Survivors Surrender 123 Search Web Search",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Polonnaruwa - 599 fugitives have been arrested after surrendering till this evening during the unrest following the suspicious death of a prisoner at the Kandakadu Rehabilitation Center under the Welikanda Police Division.",
        "However, police and the army are still searching for 126 more fugitives, police said.",
        "The body of the deceased has been taken to the Polonnaruwa General Hospital for autopsy.",
        "Commissioner General of Rehabilitation Major General Darshana Hettiarachchi said that 997 drug addicts were being detained at the Kandakadu Rehabilitation Center during the unrest.",
        "Police spokesman Senior Superintendent of Police Nihal Taltuwa said special inquiries were underway into the suspicious death of a detainee and the escape of detainees detained on a court order.",
        "It is noteworthy that these investigations are taking place under Polonnaruwa Senior Police Inspector Oshan Hewavidharana."
      ],
